# Full Send — AmphetamineXL Deploy Checklist

When the user says "full send", "deploy this", or "fully deploy", execute every step below in order. Do not skip steps. Do not mark done until `pgrep` and `gh release view` both pass.

---

## Pre-flight

- Confirm the new version number (e.g. `v1.1`)
- Confirm a one-line release description

---

## Step 1 — Bump version in create-dmg.sh

Open `create-dmg.sh` and update both version strings in the inline `Info.plist` block:

```xml
<key>CFBundleVersion</key>
<string>X.Y</string>
<key>CFBundleShortVersionString</key>
<string>X.Y</string>
```

---

## Step 2 — Update CHANGELOG.md

Add a new entry at the top of `CHANGELOG.md`:

```markdown
## vX.Y — YYYY-MM-DD
- <change 1>
- <change 2>
```

---

## Step 3 — Commit

Stage and commit all changes:

```bash
git add create-dmg.sh CHANGELOG.md <any other changed files>
git commit -m "vX.Y: <short description>"
```

---

## Step 4 — Create GitHub release BEFORE pushing

CI uploads the DMG to the most recent release. Create it first:

```bash
gh release create vX.Y \
  --title "vX.Y — <title>" \
  --notes "- Change one\n- Change two"
```

Verify it exists:

```bash
gh release view vX.Y
```

---

## Step 5 — Push to main (triggers CI)

```bash
git push origin main
```

CI workflow (`.github/workflows/release.yml`) will:
1. Build the Release binary via `xcodebuild`
2. Run `create-dmg.sh` to package it
3. Upload `AmphetamineXL.dmg` to the latest GitHub release

Watch CI: `gh run watch` or check GitHub Actions tab.

---

## Step 6 — Build locally and install

Build:

```bash
DEVELOPER_DIR=/Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer \
  xcodebuild -scheme AmphetamineXL -configuration Release \
  -destination "platform=macOS" build
```

Find binary and install:

```bash
BINARY=$(find ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/DerivedData -path "*/Release/AmphetamineXL" -type f 2>/dev/null | head -1)
echo "Binary: $BINARY"

pkill -x AmphetamineXL 2>/dev/null || true
sleep 1

cp "$BINARY" /Applications/AmphetamineXL.app/Contents/MacOS/AmphetamineXL

# Update Info.plist to match new version
/usr/libexec/PlistBuddy -c "Set :CFBundleVersion X.Y" /Applications/AmphetamineXL.app/Contents/Info.plist
/usr/libexec/PlistBuddy -c "Set :CFBundleShortVersionString X.Y" /Applications/AmphetamineXL.app/Contents/Info.plist

open /Applications/AmphetamineXL.app
```

---

## Step 7 — Verify (required — do not skip)

```bash
pgrep -x AmphetamineXL   # Must print a PID
gh release view vX.Y      # Must show AmphetamineXL.dmg as an asset
```

Both checks must pass. Show the output to the user.

---

## Common Failures

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| CI upload fails | Release didn't exist when push happened | Create release first, then push |
| App doesn't launch | Binary not signed or quarantine flag | `xattr -dr com.apple.quarantine /Applications/AmphetamineXL.app` |
| `pgrep` returns nothing | Binary crashed on launch | Check Console.app for crash logs |
| Wrong version shown | Info.plist not updated | Run PlistBuddy commands from Step 6 |
